snippet.title: Dealing with annoying Rivers Of Blood PvP
snippet.description:
Rivers of blood is stressful to deal with ESPECIALLY when multiple duo's use it on you. This guy ran away and came back constantly for about 9 minutes, it was annoying dealing with these people.
